Registration
************

   FastCache is released under the concept of Shareware.  If after a 3
month trial period you still wish to use FastCache I would appreciate
$20 in either NZ, Australian or American dollars.  The Australian and US
prices (both being $20) may seem artificially higher, but this covers
the cost of changing the funds to $NZ.  By registering you may not
necessarily gain anything.  However, if I get enough support I will
improve (yes, I can improve it further) FastCache.  If this is the
case, I will attempt to notify all registered users.

   Please send this completed form to:

